            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-200 mb-6 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                I work with teams to stabilise unreliable legacy systems, reduce technical debt, and bring systems up to modern security and performance standards.
            </p>
            <p class="text-charcoal-200 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">
                You get predictable behaviour in production, smoother more frequent releases, and a platform that's easier to maintain and evolve over time.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Featured Case Study -->
