        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-16 items-center">
            <div>
                <div class="text-accent-500 font-medium mb-2 text-sm sm:text-base">FEATURED CASE STUDY</div>
                <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4 sm:mb-6">
                    Hydro International - Internal Systems Modernisation
                </h2>
                <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-charcoal-200 mb-4 sm:mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Brought in to modernise Hydro International's internal project tracking systems ahead of a security audit. The platform consisted of a classic ASP application alongside an ageing Ruby on Rails system with growing operational risk.
                </p>
                <div class="space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-shield-halved text-accent-500 mr-3 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span class="text-charcoal-200 text-sm sm:text-base">Legacy stabilisation ahead of security audit</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-code-branch text-accent-500 mr-3 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span class="text-charcoal-200 text-sm sm:text-base">Strangler-fig migration pattern</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center">
                        <i class="fa-solid fa-layer-group text-accent-500 mr-3 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span class="text-charcoal-200 text-sm sm:text-base">Platform consolidation across multiple technologies</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <%= link_to case_studies_path, class: "inline-flex items-center text-accent-500 hover:text-accent-400 font-medium" do %>
                    View all case studies <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right ml-2"></i>
                <% end %>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-charcoal-700 border border-charcoal-600 p-6 sm:p-8 rounded-lg">
                <div class="space-y-4 sm:space-y-6">
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-accent-600 pl-4">
                        <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-1">THE CHALLENGE</div>
                        <div class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">Years of accumulated technical debt, fragile behaviour, and security concerns made a direct rewrite risky</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-charcoal-600 pl-4">
                        <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-1">THE APPROACH</div>
                        <div class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">Stabilised key issues first, then introduced a new application in parallel using a strangler-fig approach</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="border-l-4 border-charcoal-600 pl-4">
                        <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-1">THE OUTCOME</div>
                        <div class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">A smooth migration with minimal disruption that met audit requirements</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

